delete Makefile and run ```cmake CMakeLists.txt``` if makefile does not work to make new makefile
Makefile works in Ubuntu so there is no reason for it to not work

look in main.c entity/entity.h entity/entity.c

--numtrainers will never crash when a reasonable amount of memory is available
the only bug I know of is I don't know what the timer will do after 600 hours of runtime
